</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【試玩】Switch 版《 PUL PUL 天竺鼠車車》    4 人合作對戰小遊戲</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/19/pulpul/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=pulpul</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jonathan]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jan 2022 08:54:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[倉鼠]]></category><category><![CDATA[天竺鼠車車]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1081876</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近來天竺鼠車車興起，牠們憑著可愛的設計，無厘頭但同時有教育意義的故事短片，成功吸引大量粉絲熱愛。現在就為各位介 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近來天竺鼠車車興起，牠們憑著可愛的設計，無厘頭但同時有教育意義的故事短片，成功吸引大量粉絲熱愛。現在就為各位介紹由 Bandai 推出的 Switch 遊戲作品，《 PUL PUL 天竺鼠車車：一起來天竺鼠車車派對》，讓各位回憶倉鼠非常可愛，不要隨便處理他們。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271873965_216218690700415_2384365469681171683_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271873965_216218690700415_2384365469681171683_n-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271873965_216218690700415_2384365469681171683_n-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271873965_216218690700415_2384365469681171683_n-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271873965_216218690700415_2384365469681171683_n.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>由 Bandai 推出的《 PUL PUL 天竺鼠車車：一起來天竹鼠車車派對》（下簡稱遊戲），主要是一款排隊類型的遊戲作品，類似 Mario Party，有多款可以 4 人線上／離線合作或對決的小遊戲 mini games，讓你與好友一同遊玩。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n-1280x729.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n-768x437.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n-1536x875.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/271927135_615215296429828_5957696868191253650_n.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>當中有不少有趣的小遊戲，例如踢足球，123 紅綠燈、音樂節奏反應遊戲、障礙賽等多款遊戲，玩家可以因應不同遊戲作品，組隊合作或獨立每一位玩家，並設定不同的規則，一決勝負。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-896.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-896-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-896-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-896-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-896.jpg 1275w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-897.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081902" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-897-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-897-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-897-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-897.jpg 1276w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>踢足球，分兩隊玩家比賽，用頭撞擊巨型足球，撞中對方龍門就可以了</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-886.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-886-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-886-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-886-768x429.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-886.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-887.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-887-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-887-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-887-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-887.jpg 1271w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>123 紅綠燈，要觀察女主角何時起床，然後馬上迴避躲藏起來</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-885.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-885-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-885-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-885-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-885.jpg 1276w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-884.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-884-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-884-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-884-768x430.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-884.jpg 1278w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>音樂節奏反應，要你掌握節奏，快速記下正確按鍵，再按拍子節奏重新輸入一次</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-888.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081898" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-888-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-888-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-888-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-888.jpg 1278w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>障礙賽，你需要逃避後方的攻擊，並跨國不同的障礙物，到達終點</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-891.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081899" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-891-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-891-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-891-768x429.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-891.jpg 1281w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-890.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-890-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-890-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-890-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-890.jpg 1272w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>還有賽車，先到先贏（迷之聲：哦，唔通遲到嗰個贏咩？）</p><p>當然亦有大量的角色選項，你可以選取後按個人喜好，戴上各款裝飾，創造出獨特的天竺鼠角色進行遊戲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-892.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081903" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-892-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-892-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-892-768x429.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-892.jpg 1276w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-893.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081904" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-893-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-893-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-893-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-893.jpg 1272w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-894.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081905" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-894-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-894-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-894-768x431.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-894.jpg 1279w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-895.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1081906" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-895-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-895-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-895-768x430.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/BR2017-895.jpg 1274w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>派對遊戲雖然是「破壞友情類」或「情侶廝殺」的最佳選擇（誤），但作品中可以看到，牠們非常可愛，雖然與倉鼠不同，但都是有生命，不會主動傷害人類，所以不要將大門放入膠袋，「處理」牠們啊。</p><p>遊戲名稱：《 PUL PUL 天竹鼠車車：一起來天竹鼠車車派對》<br />類型：線上休閒<br />推出日期：已推出<br />平台：Nintendo Switch</p></p><div class="feedflare">
